{"tid":254123,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"80後炒樓狂人教路　鬼節結婚算到盡","createTime":"2017-05-23T02:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T07:08:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d032dd14fb7fa331b08a4df55496cdbc1fc76f4e","tid":254123,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T02:57:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=DVeImgqIMDg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDVeImgqIMDg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=MIbL8IPx8DoPDBbnzfpd9aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=c7769b8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=DVeImgqIMDg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\nE週刊 E Media Plus 觀看次數：4,379<br />\n訂閱2.2萬<br />\n63<br />\n發佈日期：2016年8月24日新鴻基地產（00016）旗下元朗樓盤Grand YOHO開賣在即，地產代理間近日流傳一張穿着校服少女，在售樓處簽名入票的相片。即使大家都相信她只是代父母辦理入票手續，但已引來坊間熱議，果真「成功需父幹」？其實不然，早在4年前就曾出現數位「80後」炒樓狂人。<br />\n<br />\n這班80後樓神如今手持數個物業，更著書立說、開辦講座，當中以「80後樓神」自居的吳龍飛繼續密炒港島樓及裝修劏房。眼見年輕人要花費大量資金在結婚及上車，吳龍飛便提出一套另類結婚方案。<br />\n<br />\ne+官網：<a href=\"http://eweekly.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feweekly.hk&d=MIbL8IPx8DoPDBbnzfpd9aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7a628674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://eweekly.hk</a><br />\nFB專頁：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EMediaPlusHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEMediaPlusHK%2F&d=MIbL8IPx8DoPDBbnzfpd9aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=fed5702f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EMediaPlusHK/</a><br />\n類別<br />\n人物與網誌<br />\n授權<br />\n標準 YouTube 授權"},{"pid":"64b845d6f5e82305cbf998ffeb4f012d4d77d8fa","tid":254123,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c349498fcf62f632e201e86f2996ed51511f8b","tid":254123,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T02:35:26.000Z","